WEBVTT

00:00:58.517 --> 00:01:02.810
wa jinsi kimelea
kilivyo na utata.

00:01:03.365 --> 00:01:05.992
Hata hivyo, licha ya hili,

00:01:06.016 --> 00:01:11.516
mbinu yetu ya kubuni chanjo
imebakia kuwa ya msingi.

00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:16.460
Kutengeneza chanjo nzuri,
tunalazimika kurudi kwenye misingi

00:01:16.484 --> 00:01:21.009
kuelewa jinsi miili yetu ina
shughulikia huu utata.

00:01:22.460 --> 00:01:26.657
Watu wanaoambukizwa na
malaria mara kwa mara

00:01:26.681 --> 00:01:28.148
hujifunza kukabiliana nayo.

00:01:28.689 --> 00:01:31.990
Wanapata maambukizi,
lakini hawaumwi.